{"tid":2358422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"智珉退出AOA近況首曝光！「關在家裡誰都不見」好友4字形容狀態","createTime":"2021-01-08T06:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T08:58:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7bfa6c115bd98da1633bb95e0cef09dcef408e","tid":2358422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"韓星智珉（지민）曾是團體AOA的隊長，日前因為和珉娥（민아）的糾紛被翻出因此退團，去年7月4日寫下道歉文後就毫無音訊，近日有韓媒透露了她的近況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5383/d5383776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5383%2Fd5383776.jpg&h=72024441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉近況曝光。（圖／翻攝自智珉IG）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《dailian》報導，智珉被冠上「霸凌者」的標籤後過著與外部斷絕的生活，不只經紀人就連其他朋友都不見面，和她很好的朋友們都說智珉現在是「閉門不出」的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，AOA於2019年參加《Queendom》以亮眼表現獲得關注，同年更以迷你六輯《NEW MOON》回歸，怎料2020年卻爆出前成員珉娥指控遭到霸凌的消息，就這樣團體活動沒了音訊，智珉退出後，酉奈（유나）在2021年1月1日合約到期不續約，現在團內僅剩惠晶（혜정）、雪炫（설현）和澯美（찬미）在FNC娛樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5383/d5383777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5383%2Fd5383777.jpg&h=bea844df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉（中）和酉奈（右一）接續離開FNC娛樂。（圖／翻攝自AOA臉書）"},{"pid":"38af99aae274e86351b83c2506eddb547fd9c77b","tid":2358422,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"到依家我都無聽過女團啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845fe7a24925c3c5d946c19b13e6ca92b2dd7638","tid":2358422,"uid":133223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38af99aae274e86351b83c2506eddb547fd9c77b","tid":2358422,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"到依家我都無聽過女團啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a